conference_notes: Partnerships provide an opportunity to leverage data use toward sustainability initiatives. Collaborations with different partners and with users mean that everybody is able to develop a tool for environmental action.
name: Leveraging Data Visualization and Partnerships for Environmental Action
info: The key point of this meet will the discussion about the ability to extract data from different websites, the ability to upload these images and connecting with the community.
